\textbf{Table~\ref{tab:expected}:} Expected Attack Success Rate---Full Defense vs. Baselines.

\begin{table}[h]
\centering
\caption{ASR: Full Defense vs.~baselines (mean $\pm$ 95\% CI, $\alpha=0.5$).}
\label{tab:expected}
\small
